text: The 1986 Camus Thailand Masters was a professional non-ranking snooker tournament held in August 1986 in Bangkok, Thailand. 16 year-old local favorite James Wattana won the tournament, defeating Terry Griffiths 2–1 in the final. ==Main draw== ==References== Category:1986 in snooker Category:1986 in Thai sport Category:Sport in Thailand
title: 1986 Thailand Masters
